    image: "./blogs/7-facial-care-tips-for-men.jpg",
    slug: "7-facial-care-tips-for-men",
    intro: "The days when seeming untidy was a mark of manliness are long gone. You don't need to get mani-pedis to be a manly man; women want a man who keeps himself clean and maintained. And while there is a tonne of information available on beauty advice for women, there isn't as much for males. Men, you too need a skin care routine. It's not just for women. Male skin needs additional care in addition to washing and moisturising. You must adhere to this simple skin care routine to prevent dry, dull, and brittle skin. Here is a list of helpful grooming advice for men that we have put together",
